      the drop.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915777
    m_Localized: Recover Rations
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915778
    m_Localized: Stack a Recruit on the Supply Cache to pull a usable Ration Pack.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915779
    m_Localized: Strip Circuit Parts
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915780
    m_Localized: Work the Rubble Slab until you recover Circuit Parts.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915781
    m_Localized: Sell Salvage
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915782
    m_Localized: Drag any spare card into the recycler terminal and take Credits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915783
    m_Localized: Buy Utility
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915784
    m_Localized: Spend Credits on a District Utility Crate to widen your options.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915785
    m_Localized: Scavenge Scrap
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915786
    m_Localized: Send a Recruit into the Scrap Heap and recover basic Scrap.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915787
    m_Localized: Brace Scrap Stock
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915788
    m_Localized: Process Scrap into Reinforced Scrap for stronger builds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915789
    m_Localized: Shape a Signal Rod
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9155915790
    m_Localized: Turn Reinforced Scrap into a Signal Rod for relay work.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110080
    m_Localized: Freeze the Clock
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110081
    m_Localized: Click the time control twice to pause the district before it runs
      ahead of you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110082
    m_Localized: Seed a Supply Cache
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110083
    m_Localized: Stack a Ration Pack on a Nutrient Bed to prepare another Supply
      Cache.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110084
    m_Localized: Hold Four Rations
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110085
    m_Localized: Keep four Ration Packs on the board before the next hunger cycle.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110086
    m_Localized: Build a Hab Pod
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110087
    m_Localized: Construct a Hab Pod so civilians can survive inside the fortress
      line.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110088
    m_Localized: Expand the Crew
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110089
    m_Localized: Maintain at least two Recruits. One pair of hands is not a district.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110090
    m_Localized: Protect a Dependent
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110091
    m_Localized: Place two Recruits in a Hab Pod and register a Dependent.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110092
    m_Localized: Raise a Recruit
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110093
    m_Localized: Keep the Dependent in a Hab Pod long enough to become a Recruit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110094
    m_Localized: Staff the District
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9160110095
    m_Localized: Maintain three Recruits. The Kernel needs a real crew, not a rumor.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9172692992
    m_Localized: First Contact
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9172692993
    m_Localized: Defeat a Null Anomaly before it spreads through the board.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9172692994
    m_Localized: Open the Memory Pit
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9172692995
    m_Localized: Construct access to the Memory Pit for bodies, drives, and old debts.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9172692996
    m_Localized: Claim the Vessel
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9172692997
    m_Localized: Bring down a Blackout Cultist and recover its forbidden hardware.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9172692998
    m_Localized: Build the Conduit
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9172692999
    m_Localized: Construct the Blacksite Conduit. It is dangerous, but it reaches
      systems nobody else can.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9172693000
    m_Localized: Start the Root Rite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9172693001
    m_Localized: Place the Bloodchrome Vessel on the Blacksite Conduit and force
      a response.
