  - m_Id: 1728643667341316
    m_Localized: Night 1
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1728643667341317
    m_Localized: Signal anomaly at the perimeter. Three crawler-class processes moving
      toward the core. Run standard suppression protocol.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1728643667341318
    m_Localized: Night 2
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1728643667341319
    m_Localized: Mixed intrusion pattern. Fast-signal fragments outpacing the primary
      crawlers. Prioritize the runners before they reach the core.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1728643667341320
    m_Localized: Night 3
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1728643667341321
    m_Localized: Heavy assault pattern confirmed. Armored bug-class units flanked
      by fast fragments. They are testing the core directly.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1728643667341322
    m_Localized: Night 4
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1728643667341323
    m_Localized: Something new on the grid. Slower. Heavier. It doesn't panic when
      you hit it. Get your defenders in position before it reaches the core.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1728643667341324
    m_Localized: Night 5
    m_Metadata:
